- This is Olbricht.
- It's been 3 hours Olbricht.

738
01:16:22,906 --> 01:16:24,501
What the hell
have you been doing?

739
01:16:24,502 --> 01:16:27,351
We've had no confirmation
that Hitler was dead.

740
01:16:27,352 --> 01:16:28,656
Damn-it!

741
01:16:28,657 --> 01:16:31,149
I saw the explosion myself!

742
01:16:31,150 --> 01:16:33,844
- We are committed.
- Dear god.

743
01:16:33,845 --> 01:16:36,355
Now where is Fromm?
Is he with us?

744
01:16:36,356 --> 01:16:39,834
- Is he with us?
- No one has spoken to him yet.

745
01:16:51,177 --> 01:16:55,189
Listen to me. Never mind Germany,
never mind Europe.

746
01:16:55,190 --> 01:16:57,298
Your life... is at stake now.

747
01:16:57,299 --> 01:16:58,718
And if you wanna live
through the night,

748
01:16:58,719 --> 01:16:59,876
you'll do exactly as I say.

749
01:16:59,877 --> 01:17:03,027
The second you hang up the phone
initiate Valkyrie in Fromm's name.

750
01:17:03,028 --> 01:17:04,617
Give him the choice to join us...

751
01:17:04,618 --> 01:17:06,835
or place him under immediate arrest,
you understand me?

752
01:17:06,836 --> 01:17:08,090
Yes.

753
01:17:08,091 --> 01:17:11,324
I'll be at Fromm's office
in 15 minutes. Be there when I arrive.

754
01:17:40,830 --> 01:17:44,714
Call Beck and others.
Tell them it's time.

755
01:17:49,293 --> 01:17:51,959
Put me through
to communications.

756
01:17:52,758 --> 01:17:56,655
This is General Olbricht.
Calling on behalf of General Fromm...

757
01:17:56,656 --> 01:18:00,712
Commander of the reserve army.
The Führer, Adolf Hitler, is dead.

758
01:18:00,713 --> 01:18:02,346
A group of radicals in the SS...

759
01:18:02,347 --> 01:18:04,791
are attempting to seize control
of the government.

760
01:18:04,792 --> 01:18:08,260
Initiate operation Valkyrie.

761
01:18:41,624 --> 01:18:45,392
You have your orders.
Pass them along.

762
01:19:20,764 --> 01:19:22,771
Battalion.

763
01:19:22,772 --> 01:19:24,611
Attention!

764
01:19:28,862 --> 01:19:30,661
The Führer...

765
01:19:32,462 --> 01:19:36,463
Our Führer, Adolf Hitler...

766
01:19:38,010 --> 01:19:40,611
is dead.

767
01:19:40,612 --> 01:19:42,727
Who told you
the Führer was dead?

768
01:19:42,728 --> 01:19:45,462
General Fellgiebel,
at the Wolf's Lair.

769
01:19:47,421 --> 01:19:50,334
There's no use calling.
All communication lines are down.

770
01:19:50,335 --> 01:19:52,413
Get me the Wolf's Lair.

771
01:19:56,435 --> 01:19:57,755
Wolf's Lair.

772
01:19:57,756 --> 01:20:01,545
Yes, General Fromm for
Fieldmarshall Keitel, urgent.

773
01:20:05,331 --> 01:20:08,784
- Keitel.
- I'm sorry to... huh, disturb you, sir.

774
01:20:08,785 --> 01:20:10,221
But I wonder if you could tell me
what's happening?

775
01:20:10,222 --> 01:20:12,270
The most incredible rumours
are circulating in Berlin.

776
01:20:12,271 --> 01:20:14,021
I don't know what you mean.

777
01:20:14,022 --> 01:20:18,165
There's talk that the Führer
has been assassinated.

778
01:20:19,080 --> 01:20:24,040
Another failed attempt.
The Führer was never in danger.

779
01:20:24,041 --> 01:20:27,817
By the way, where's your man,Stauffenberg?

780
01:20:27,818 --> 01:20:31,752
Stauffenberg? On his way back
to Berlin, I would think.

781
01:20:31,753 --> 01:20:36,157
Let me know when he arrives.
I'd like a word with him.

782
01:20:42,508 --> 01:20:44,849
- The Führer's fine.
- That is a lie.

783
01:20:44,850 --> 01:20:47,455
Adolf Hitler is dead.
Operation Valkyrie is in effect.

784
01:20:47,456 --> 01:20:49,146
Only I can initiate Valkyrie.

785
01:20:49,147 --> 01:20:51,002
You did.

786
01:20:59,322 --> 01:21:00,657
This is treason...

787
01:21:00,658 --> 01:21:03,277
Right now, the reserve army
is assuming control of Berlin.

788
01:21:03,278 --> 01:21:05,110
Are you with us or not?

789
01:21:05,111 --> 01:21:07,039
Do you realise what you've done?

790
01:21:07,040 --> 01:21:08,932
The Führer is alive.

791
01:21:08,933 --> 01:21:13,131
I delivered the bomb myself,
I saw the blast. He is dead.

792
01:21:14,561 --> 01:21:15,640
Are you with us or not?

793
01:21:15,641 --> 01:21:17,820
I don't believe this is happening.
This is some kind of...

794
01:21:17,821 --> 01:21:19,339
Are you with us or not?

795
01:21:19,340 --> 01:21:25,506
Colonel, if what you say is true
you should shoot yourself immediately.

796
01:21:25,507 --> 01:21:26,944
The rest of you are under arrest.

797
01:21:26,945 --> 01:21:29,082
No General, you are.

798
01:21:34,091 --> 01:21:37,488
I don't know
where you think this is going.

799
01:21:39,643 --> 01:21:41,443
Get me operations.

800
01:21:42,557 --> 01:21:43,998
This is Colonel Stauffenberg,

801
01:21:43,999 --> 01:21:46,533
seal off the War Ministery
per operation Valkyrie.

802
01:21:46,534 --> 01:21:47,793
No one gets in or out...

803
01:21:47,794 --> 01:21:50,893
without authorization
from General Olbricht's office.

804
01:22:06,576 --> 01:22:08,376
General Beck.

805
01:22:08,869 --> 01:22:10,894
You're not wearing your uniform, sir.

806
01:22:10,895 --> 01:22:13,922
This should be seen
as a movement of the people.

807
01:22:19,807 --> 01:22:22,252
Colonel Stauffenberg?

808
01:22:22,253 --> 01:22:24,720
Yes.

809
01:22:27,226 --> 01:22:30,830
The chief has guaranteed
the full support of the Berlin police.

810
01:22:32,792 --> 01:22:37,510
You will have no interference
from my men, you have my word.

811
01:22:39,601 --> 01:22:41,525
Thank you.

812
01:23:15,406 --> 01:23:19,174
Colonel Stauffenberg, sir.
We are reporting for duty.

813
01:23:23,869 --> 01:23:26,101
Thanks for coming.

814
01:23:30,135 --> 01:23:31,934
Gentlemen...

815
01:23:31,935 --> 01:23:33,934
in 3 hours I want confirmation...

816
01:23:33,935 --> 01:23:35,917
that the government quarters
is ours,

817
01:23:35,918 --> 01:23:39,359
and SS command has been cleared
of every living soul.

818
01:23:39,601 --> 01:23:41,837
You all know what must be done.

819
01:23:42,320 --> 01:23:48,209
By nightfall I wanna know that Hitler's
Germany has seen it's last sunrise.

820
01:24:15,731 --> 01:24:17,501
Yes sir, the broadcast
has been approved.

821
01:24:17,502 --> 01:24:20,238
Feldmarschall Witzleben
has been appointed...

822
01:24:20,239 --> 01:24:23,175
commander in chief
of the armed forces.

823
01:24:23,176 --> 01:24:25,308
That's exactly
why he's been appointed...

824
01:24:25,309 --> 01:24:27,424
if he was a member of the Party
he'd be locked up as a suspect.

825
01:24:27,425 --> 01:24:29,205
Yes sir, I understand.
This is an emergency.

826
01:24:29,206 --> 01:24:31,401
Commanding officer
of the 11th district...

827
01:24:31,402 --> 01:24:33,031
I need a decision, Major.

828
01:24:33,032 --> 01:24:35,399
Tell your men that acts of
vengeance will not be tolerated.

829
01:24:35,400 --> 01:24:37,308
Connect me to the commanding
officer in Hannover...

830
01:24:37,309 --> 01:24:39,315
We represent a different
form of government.

831
01:24:39,316 --> 01:24:42,308
I'd be careful who you said that to.
Loyalty to the Party isn't what it used to be.

832
01:24:42,309 --> 01:24:44,001
Yes, Paris, France.

833
01:24:44,002 --> 01:24:46,049
Heads of state
murdered the Führer.

834
01:24:46,050 --> 01:24:47,155
Thank you,

835
01:24:47,156 --> 01:24:49,329
you made the right decision.

836
01:24:49,830 --> 01:24:51,868
District 13 is ours.

837
01:25:02,706 --> 01:25:07,183
You're under arrest
for crimes against the state.

838
01:25:15,736 --> 01:25:18,219
This is Stauffenberg, I'm trying
to connect with Major-General Todt.

839
01:25:18,220 --> 01:25:21,134
...413 battalion,
you have no trouble getting...

840
01:25:21,135 --> 01:25:24,319
...This is Colonel Stauffenberg...
... will explain everything...

841
01:25:24,320 --> 01:25:26,319
Excellent.

842
01:25:27,631 --> 01:25:29,798
My wife is at Bamberg
with my children,

843
01:25:29,799 --> 01:25:32,394
would you please try
to reach them with the phone?

844
01:25:32,395 --> 01:25:33,795
Thank you.

845
01:25:33,796 --> 01:25:37,001
General Scheidler has issued the Valkyrie
orders and has sealed off headquarters.

846
01:25:37,002 --> 01:25:41,031
Check the radio stations every 20 minutes
until we have confirmation they're ours.

847
01:25:52,831 --> 01:25:55,296
With all due respect, sir.
You can't believe everything you hear.

848
01:25:55,297 --> 01:25:57,497
That is SS propaganda, he's dead.

849
01:25:57,498 --> 01:26:00,304
The commander of the home army
is authorized to give orders.

850
01:26:01,140 --> 01:26:02,900
General?

851
01:26:04,759 --> 01:26:06,298
Our men in the transport office
have secured...

852
01:26:06,299 --> 01:26:07,872
the railways
communications network.

853
01:26:07,873 --> 01:26:10,403
...repeat to stations...

854
01:26:11,520 --> 01:26:15,078
- ... we need more men...
- I'm glad you showed up.

855
01:26:15,079 --> 01:26:17,272
He's with us.

856
01:26:17,323 --> 01:26:20,924
Mertz, call Potsdam, tell them place
all available units under our control.

857
01:26:20,925 --> 01:26:22,779
You have your men,
now get control...

858
01:26:22,780 --> 01:26:24,732
We have control
of the government quarter.

859
01:26:24,733 --> 01:26:26,962
We don't have Berlin yet.

860
01:26:48,703 --> 01:26:51,676
- What is it now, Sergeant?
- Arrest orders, sir.

861
01:26:51,677 --> 01:26:53,734
One from Colonel Stauffenberg
in the War Ministry.

862
01:26:53,735 --> 01:26:55,590
To arrest Reichsminister Göbbels.

863
01:26:55,591 --> 01:27:00,825
The other is from the Wolfs Lair
to arrest Colonel Stauffenberg.

864
01:27:05,326 --> 01:27:07,617
Send them both through.

865
01:27:08,119 --> 01:27:11,165
Our job is not to interpret orders.

866
01:27:11,166 --> 01:27:13,697
Our job is to pass them
along, regardless...

867
01:27:13,698 --> 01:27:17,007
- Yes, but...
- That will be all, Sergeant.

868
01:27:51,629 --> 01:27:55,940
New arrest orders, sir.
For Stauffenberg and Göbbels.

869
01:27:56,527 --> 01:27:59,379
Do we arrest them both?

870
01:27:59,380 --> 01:28:02,238
I would hate to find out
I am being taken advantage of.

871
01:28:02,239 --> 01:28:06,079
- You really think it's a coup?
- I'm afraid so.

872
01:28:06,080 --> 01:28:08,903
But I can't say which side we're on.

873
01:28:09,424 --> 01:28:11,684
Come with me.

874
01:28:21,237 --> 01:28:23,247
I've just spoken to Colonel...

875
01:28:23,248 --> 01:28:27,085
They've arrested 1200 SS
and Gestapo officials in Paris.

876
01:28:27,086 --> 01:28:29,075
Not a single shot fired.

877
01:28:29,076 --> 01:28:33,201
Early reports from Vienna are good.
I'm waiting on word from Prague.

878
01:29:06,204 --> 01:29:08,876
I'm ready to be connected.

879
01:29:21,640 --> 01:29:23,608
Minister Göbbels?

880
01:29:23,609 --> 01:29:25,498
What can I do for you, Major?

881
01:29:25,499 --> 01:29:28,835
My battalion has an order to block
every government quarter,

882
01:29:28,836 --> 01:29:32,072
and place you under arrest.

883
01:29:33,846 --> 01:29:37,325
Are you a dedicated
National-Socialist, Major?

884
01:29:38,426 --> 01:29:40,695
Yes, Sir.

885
01:29:52,804 --> 01:29:56,211
Major Remer here.

886
01:29:56,212 --> 01:29:58,294
Hello.

887
01:29:59,395 --> 01:30:03,258
Do you recognize my voice?

888
01:30:03,851 --> 01:30:07,783
- Yes, my Führer.
- Then listen to me very carefully.

889
01:30:09,578 --> 01:30:13,048
I want these traitors taken alive.

890
01:30:13,049 --> 01:30:16,997
Yes, my Führer.

891
01:30:20,292 --> 01:30:25,463
You heard what he said. The Führer
wants the traitors taken alive.

892
01:30:25,820 --> 01:30:28,380
Yes, sir.

893
01:30:51,890 --> 01:30:53,933
It is a coup alright.

894
01:30:53,934 --> 01:30:57,494
We can't afford
to remain neutral any longer.

895
01:30:59,922 --> 01:31:03,221
You have to make a decision.

896
01:31:04,293 --> 01:31:08,028
When it's over we better land
on the right side.

897
01:31:13,890 --> 01:31:15,996
We better.

898
01:31:17,681 --> 01:31:19,853
Send through all communication
with the Wolf's Lair.

899
01:31:19,854 --> 01:31:22,699
Stop all communications
with Stauffenberg.

900
01:31:28,355 --> 01:31:29,920
Release these men.

901
01:31:29,921 --> 01:31:31,404
Why, sir?

902
01:31:31,405 --> 01:31:33,280
they're part of the coup.

903
01:31:33,281 --> 01:31:36,213
I've just been on the phone
with Hitler himself.

904
01:31:36,214 --> 01:31:39,132
We are the coup
We've been duped.

905
01:31:41,937 --> 01:31:45,084
We've lost contact with district 11.

906
01:31:47,449 --> 01:31:51,578
The switchboard is overloaded.
Give it ten minutes, then try again.

907
01:31:55,325 --> 01:31:58,145
Give me General Vieler, district 11.

908
01:31:58,146 --> 01:32:02,494
- We still need our...
- Keep trying.

909
01:32:03,869 --> 01:32:06,266
Where is General Fromm?

910
01:32:07,807 --> 01:32:11,188
General Fromm is no longer
in command, I am.

911
01:32:12,493 --> 01:32:14,012
Beck, what are you doing here?
What is going on?

912
01:32:14,013 --> 01:32:15,431
The Führer is dead.

913
01:32:15,432 --> 01:32:17,063
The SS are staging a coup,

914
01:32:17,064 --> 01:32:18,660
initiated operation Valkyrie...

915
01:32:18,661 --> 01:32:21,219
To crush the uprising
and save Hitler's Germany.

916
01:32:21,220 --> 01:32:23,992
You'll present the order
to your troops.

917
01:32:24,493 --> 01:32:27,657
I will do no such thing
until I speak to General Fromm.

918
01:32:27,658 --> 01:32:31,496
You'll follow your orders
or you are arrested.

919
01:32:31,826 --> 01:32:34,459
This is treason.

920
01:32:34,504 --> 01:32:38,511
I will take no part.
The Führer is not dead.

921
01:32:38,843 --> 01:32:40,666
- The Führer is not dead!
- Stop him!

922
01:32:40,667 --> 01:32:44,274
The Führer is not dead!
The Führer is not dead!

923
01:32:44,275 --> 01:32:49,114
I sworn an oath! This is treason!
You all sworn an oath!

924
01:32:49,115 --> 01:32:54,005
Listen to what I have to say!
You are all making a terrible mistake!

925
01:32:54,006 --> 01:32:57,454
The Führer is not dead!

926
01:32:58,772 --> 01:33:01,659
The Führer is not dead!

927
01:33:02,340 --> 01:33:04,775
Please, try my wife again...

928
01:33:13,385 --> 01:33:15,720
Bamberg, please...

929
01:33:21,397 --> 01:33:23,777
Take your hands off!

930
01:33:27,940 --> 01:33:30,148
Sir...

931
01:33:40,776 --> 01:33:42,947
...Over 215 enemy tanks
have been annahilated...

932
01:33:42,948 --> 01:33:44,847
in the past week alone...

933
01:33:44,848 --> 01:33:49,268
The Airforce engaged a low-flying
offensive on enemy concentrations...

934
01:33:49,513 --> 01:33:51,123
Sir? I can't get through
to General Görlock.

935
01:33:51,124 --> 01:33:54,120
Send a runner down to his office,
bring him here.

936
01:33:56,466 --> 01:33:59,005
Yes, thank you.

937
01:33:59,006 --> 01:34:01,334
Yes, this is Stauffenberg.

938
01:34:01,335 --> 01:34:03,753
I was speaking to the
General 5 minutes ago.

939
01:34:03,754 --> 01:34:05,737
He told me he'll return my call...

940
01:34:05,738 --> 01:34:09,355
I trust everything in your district
is under control.

941
01:34:12,038 --> 01:34:14,723
And the General knows I'm waiting?

942
01:34:14,724 --> 01:34:16,724
I'm ordering you to put him
on the phone immediately.

943
01:34:16,725 --> 01:34:18,775
...the army gave their oath
to a liar, Hans...

944
01:34:18,776 --> 01:34:19,775
Hello?

945
01:34:19,776 --> 01:34:21,575
...One who has broken his own oath
to the people a hundred times over...

946
01:34:21,576 --> 01:34:23,460
Hello?

947
01:34:23,461 --> 01:34:25,539
Hans, listen to me.

948
01:34:50,709 --> 01:34:54,359
This operation has been terminated!
Stand down!

949
01:34:58,781 --> 01:35:01,773
Today an attempt
was made on the Führer's life.

950
01:35:01,774 --> 01:35:06,616
The Führer himself suffered no major
injuries beyond light burns and bruises.

951
01:35:06,617 --> 01:35:08,743
He resumed his work immediately.

952
01:35:08,744 --> 01:35:15,369
No seriously wounded include General...
Colonel Brandt and staff-officer Berger...

953
01:35:19,493 --> 01:35:22,702
Send the following orders to all
reserve army commanders:

954
01:35:22,703 --> 01:35:26,411
"Broadcast incorrect.
The Führer is dead...

955
01:35:28,313 --> 01:35:30,400
Operation Valkyrie still in effect.

956
01:35:30,401 --> 01:35:36,261
Reich Marshal Goering, and has
scheduled to receive Mussolini...

957
01:35:36,262 --> 01:35:38,435
Long live our Fuhrer, Adolf Hitler,

958
01:35:38,436 --> 01:35:42,112
whom the Almighty God
has so visibly blessed today.

959
01:35:45,127 --> 01:35:47,005
I saw the blast.

960
01:35:51,545 --> 01:35:53,817
I saw the blast.

961
01:36:01,980 --> 01:36:04,775
Today an attempt was made
on the Führer's life.

962
01:36:04,776 --> 01:36:09,632
The Führer himself suffered no major
injuries beyond light burns and bruises...

963
01:36:09,633 --> 01:36:10,890
I'm sorry...

964
01:36:10,891 --> 01:36:15,390
...resumed his work immediately.
No seriously wounded...

965
01:36:39,598 --> 01:36:42,024
Stay tuned for the Fuhrer's
address to the German people.

966
01:36:42,025 --> 01:36:44,505
My family?

967
01:36:44,506 --> 01:36:47,486
Our lines have been cut.

968
01:36:50,215 --> 01:36:52,054
I'm sorry.

969
01:36:53,920 --> 01:36:55,628
Go.

970
01:36:55,925 --> 01:36:58,512
It's alright. Go.

971
01:37:13,723 --> 01:37:17,255
General, sir.
We have to get you out of here.

972
01:38:39,772 --> 01:38:41,545
Get back.

973
01:38:41,610 --> 01:38:43,657
- Stop.
- Stand down.

974
01:38:43,658 --> 01:38:46,284
- I said stop.
- I said stand down.

975
01:39:11,890 --> 01:39:14,123
Hold your fire.

976
01:39:22,364 --> 01:39:24,833
Colonel Stauffenberg.

977
01:39:26,932 --> 01:39:30,385
By orders of the Führer,
you are under arrest.

978
01:39:51,700 --> 01:39:56,577
If you have any last messages
to your wives and children,

979
01:39:56,578 --> 01:39:58,443
I will hear them now.

980
01:39:58,472 --> 01:40:01,936
Very well, a court martial
convened by me...

981
01:40:01,937 --> 01:40:03,827
in the Führer's absence,
will pronounce sentence.

982
01:40:03,828 --> 01:40:05,598
Beck, you are under arrest.

983
01:40:05,599 --> 01:40:10,835
Coronel Mertz Von Quirnheim,
General Olbricht, Tenente Hiften...

984
01:40:10,836 --> 01:40:14,458
And the Colonel, whose name I will
not mention, are condemned to death.

985
01:40:14,459 --> 01:40:16,939
General, my orders are
to take these men alive.

986
01:40:16,940 --> 01:40:18,700
Noted, Major.

987
01:40:19,932 --> 01:40:22,637
I'd like a pistol, please.

988
01:40:24,461 --> 01:40:27,126
For personal reasons.

989
01:40:43,676 --> 01:40:46,116
- Get on with it.
- With all respect, sir.

990
01:40:46,117 --> 01:40:47,691
That will be all, Major.

991
01:40:47,692 --> 01:40:49,857
Killing us won't hide
your involvement.

992
01:40:49,858 --> 01:40:52,574
My involvement?
I don't know what you're talking about?

993
01:40:52,575 --> 01:40:55,842
- You knew and did nothing.
- You're as guilty as any of us.

994
01:40:55,843 --> 01:41:00,478
- Spare me Lieutenant.
- No one will be spared.

995
01:41:14,586 --> 01:41:17,606
I'm thinking of earlier times.

996
01:41:21,871 --> 01:41:26,201
This is an outrage. It has never
before been perpetrated here.

997
01:41:26,202 --> 01:41:29,588
A Field Marshal and a General declare
that they could do things better than he...

998
01:41:29,589 --> 01:41:33,525
Who is the Füher of us all.

999
01:41:33,526 --> 01:41:36,664
You'll protest to having said this?

1000
01:41:37,026 --> 01:41:38,740
Yes.

1001
01:41:42,031 --> 01:41:46,952
My fellow Germans. I speak to you
tonight for two reasons.

1002
01:41:46,953 --> 01:41:51,914
First, so that you can hear my voice
and know that I am unhurt.

1003
01:41:51,915 --> 01:41:56,324
Second, so that you can know
the details of a crime...

1004
01:41:56,325 --> 01:41:59,148
without parallel in German history.

1005
01:41:59,396 --> 01:42:02,605
A small clique of ambitious,

1006
01:42:02,606 --> 01:42:06,315
dishonorable officers
had conspired to eliminate me.

1007
01:42:07,193 --> 01:42:09,869
Except for a few bruises and burns...

1008
01:42:09,870 --> 01:42:13,048
I was completely untouched.

1009
01:42:14,005 --> 01:42:17,340
I see in this the hand of Providence...

1010
01:42:17,864 --> 01:42:21,317
Directing me to complete my work.

1011
01:42:29,480 --> 01:42:31,752
Look them in the eye.

1012
01:42:36,071 --> 01:42:37,824
Olbricht.

1013
01:42:47,555 --> 01:42:49,844
Men, ready!

1014
01:43:02,989 --> 01:43:07,978
And we have to show the world,
that not all of us were like him.

1015
01:43:17,400 --> 01:43:18,700
Agh...

1016
01:43:18,701 --> 01:43:22,369
Fire!
Stand!

1017
01:43:42,694 --> 01:43:44,520
Stauffenberg

1018
01:43:47,090 --> 01:43:51,449
People know we put our principles
above personal gains.

1019
01:43:55,320 --> 01:43:56,629
Men, Ready!

1020
01:43:56,630 --> 01:43:58,054
Aim!

1021
01:44:11,844 --> 01:44:14,524
Stand still.

1022
01:44:20,638 --> 01:44:25,362
You may hand us over to
the executioner, but in 3 months time...

1023
01:44:25,363 --> 01:44:29,143
The disgusted and tired people
will bring you to book.

1024
01:44:29,144 --> 01:44:33,177
And drag you alive through
the dirt in the streets.

1025
01:44:33,291 --> 01:44:36,204
Take him away.

1026
01:44:40,113 --> 01:44:43,275
Men, Ready!

1027
01:44:44,573 --> 01:44:46,729
Aim!

1028
01:44:47,251 --> 01:44:49,812
- Long live sacred Germany!
- Fire.

1029
01:44:51,018 --> 01:44:52,853
Stand.

